#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:90
msgid "When enabled, synchronizes your user data, Spaces, and Space keys between devices. Enabling this increases metadata visibility of your account, which can reveal when you have joined new Spaces, although not the Spaces you have joined."
msgstr "Kada je omogućeno, sinhronizuje vaše korisničke podatke, Spaces i ključeve Space-a između uređaja. Omogućavanje ovoga povećava vidljivost metapodataka vašeg naloga, što može otkriti kada ste se pridružili novim Spaces, iako ne i Spaces-u kojima ste se pridružili."

#: src/components/modals/SpaceSettingsModal/General.tsx:281
msgid "When messages are signed, senders confirm they come from their key. When messages aren't signed, senders have plausible deniability. This setting applies to all messages in this Space."
msgstr "Kada su poruke potpisane, pošiljaoci potvrđuju da dolaze iz njihovog ključa. Kada poruke nisu potpisane, pošiljaoci imaju verovatnu negaciju. Ova postavka se primenjuje na sve poruke u ovom Space."

#: src/components/modals/ConversationSettingsModal.tsx:244
msgid "When muted, new messages won't show unread indicators or desktop notifications."
msgstr "Kada je isključeno, nove poruke neće prikazivati nepročitane indikatore ili desktop obaveštenja."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:132
msgid "When on, anyone with your Quorum address can see your display name, avatar, and bio, even outside the Spaces you share. Useful when someone DMs you and you want them to recognize who you are. Off by default."
msgstr "Kada je uključeno, svako ko ima vašu Quorum adresu može videti vaše ime za prikaz, avatar i biografiju, čak i izvan Prostora koje delite. Korisno kada vam neko pošalje direktnu poruku i želite da vas prepozna. Podrazumevano je isključeno."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:250
msgid "When on, everyone in a Space channel sees when you're typing, and you see when they're typing."
msgstr "Kada je uključeno, svi u kanalu Prostora vide kada kucate, a vi vidite kada oni kucaju."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:179
msgid "When on, senders see when their messages reach your device, and you see when yours reach theirs."
msgstr "Kada je uključeno, pošiljaoci vide kada njihove poruke stignu na vaš uređaj, a vi vidite kada vaše stignu na njihove."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:203
msgid "When on, senders see when you've read their messages, and you see when yours are read."
msgstr "Kada je uključeno, pošiljaoci vide kada ste pročitali njihove poruke, a vi vidite kada su vaše pročitane."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:273
msgid "When on, your device fetches thumbnails from YouTube for the links you send, which reveals your IP to Google. When off, recipients see a plain link instead."
msgstr "Kada je uključeno, vaš uređaj preuzima sličice sa YouTube-a za veze koje šaljete, što otkriva vašu IP adresu Google-u. Kada je isključeno, primalac vidi običnu vezu umesto toga."

#: src/components/modals/UserSettingsModal/Privacy.tsx:227
